{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["The Cloudy Mask\n\n<size=45>Chapter 6: The Truth, Pt. 2<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It's all because of that name... \"Lützow.\"","dir":1,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"bgm":"story-1","painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"actor":405020,"bgName":"bg_story_task","side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Indeed. I don't know how it came to be, but she isn't just Deutschland of the Iron Blood, she was also born as Lützow of the Northern Parliament.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Huh?! How do they know that...?!","dir":1,"side":2,"action":[{"type":"shake","y":45,"delay":0,"dur":0.2,"number":2,"x":0}],"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And not the Lützow who fought in the Great War, the one the Northern Parliament refloated...","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Her history haunts her. So she tried desperately to make herself out as the ideal image of Iron Blood so we'd accept her.","actor":403030,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... Why would she bring this up now...","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sure, she had a thing with the Northern Parliament, but she's still Deutschland. She's one of us.","actor":401010,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And we wanted to make her feel like a part of the team, but since she's kinda sensitive, we agreed to be nice to her.","actor":401010,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"......……","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"So basically, they were simply doing their best not to hurt or upset her.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Which is why we kept this a secret from her and accepted her into the Iron Blood.","actor":404020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"That's right. Above all else, she is one of us. But ironically, all our cautiousness and special treatment wound up hurting her in the end...","actor":405020,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I think she's fine the way she is right now... but I guess she should come to terms with herself, at least a little.","actor":401010,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"It might leave her feeling blue for a while, but maybe we should tell her the truth?","actor":401010,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I say we do. It's a shame to lose the arrogant Deutschland we know, but it's time she accepts herself for who she is.","actor":403030,"subActors":[{"actor":403040,"pos":{"x":1500}}],"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"hideOther":true,"bgName":"bg_story_task","dir":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"So... they pretty much admit they lied to me...","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Deutschland whispers while her shoulders tremble. Her voice lacks its signature impactful tone, instead sounding frail.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... Slave, let me go.","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"In conclusion, we should tell Deutschland the truth.","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":0.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":404020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"But how do we go about telling her that...","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":403050},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"We don't need to do anything. Right, Gneisenau?","actor":403030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I let go of Deutschland. She walks over to open the door, then steps into the salon.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"... Ah, so you knew she was listening, Eugen.","actor":404020,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Heheh, of course I knew. So, what do you plan to do with us, Deutschland?","actor":403030,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"After a brief silence, the girl raises her voice and speaks her mind.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"You will pay dearly for deceiving me for so long.","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"But... I also want to say...","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Thank you... for accepting me.","actor":403040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"DEYIZHI6","fadeOut":1.5}